summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting transmission line distribution easements over portions of Vacated Southeast 80th Street; Lot 7, Block 1, Callison's Scenic Addition to the City of Seattle; Section 28, Township 26 North, Range 5 East, W.M.; Section 28, Township 27 North, Range 5 East, W.M.; Snohomish County, and placing said easements under the jurisdiction of the City Light Department.
